'''Asyut Petroleum''' or '''Petrol Asyout''' is an [[Egypt]]ian club from the city of [[Asyut]], currently competing in the [[Egyptian Second Division]].

In 2008–2009 season, they reached the [[Egypt Cup]] semi-final, only to get knocked out on the 27th of January 2009.

