'''Club Atlético Ciclón''', most commonly known as '''Ciclón de Tarija''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] club from [[Tarija, Bolivia|Tarija]], [[Bolivia]] currently playing in the [[Liga de Fútbol Profesional Boliviano]] (LFPB). The club was founded on September 21, 1951, and they play their home games at the [[Estadio IV Centenário]]. Ciclón competed in the LFPB from 1985 until its relegation in 1995.<ref name='bolivia-results-rsssf-2011-08-25'>{{cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/tablesb/bolhist.html | title = Bolivia&nbsp;– List of Final Tables 1950–1990 | accessdate = 2012-07-03 | last = Abbink | first = Dinant  | date = 25 Aug 2011 | publisher = [[rsssf]]}}</ref> The team recently won the second division Nacional B championship and promotion to the LFPB for the 2015–16 season.

