The '''Cycling Union of Finland''' or '''SPU''' (in [[Finnish language|Finnish]]: ''Suomen Pyöräilyunioni'') is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Finland]].

The SPU is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].

