The '''Gooikse pijl''' is a [[Europe]]an [[Road bicycle racing|bicycle race]] held in and around [[Gooik]], [[Belgium]]. Since 2012, the race has been organised as a [[1.2]] event on the [[UCI Europe Tour]].

