'''Omladinski košarkaški klub Novi Pazar''' ({{lang-sr-cyrl|Омладински кошаркашки клуб Нови Пазар}}, {{lang-en|Novi Pazar Youth Basketball Club}}), commonly referred to as '''OKK Novi Pazar''' or simply '''Novi Pazar''', is a men's professional [[basketball]] [[Sports club|club]] based in [[Novi Pazar]], [[Serbia]]. They are currently competing in the [[Basketball League of Serbia]].

== History ==
In the [[2017–18 Basketball League of Serbia B|2017–18 season]], Novi Pazar placed second in the [[Basketball League of Serbia B|Second League of Serbia]] and got promoted to the [[Basketball League of Serbia]] for the [[2018–19 Basketball League of Serbia season|2018–19 season]].<ref>{{cite web|title=U Pazaru će se igrati i superligaška košarka|url=https://www.b92.net/sport/kosarka/vesti.php?yyyy=2018&mm=04&dd=21&nav_id=1384123|website=b92.net|accessdate=22 April 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sjani Pazarci preko Žarkova do elite|url=https://rtvnp.rs/2018/04/21/sjani-pazarci-preko-zarkova-do-elite/31940|website=rtvnp.rs|accessdate=22 April 2018}}</ref>

