{{use dmy dates|date=September 2014}} {{infobox country at games | NOC = ROU | NOCname = [[Romanian Olympic and Sports Committee]] | games = Summer Olympics | year = 1968 | flagcaption = | oldcode = RUM | website = {{url|www.cosr.ro }}&nbsp;{{ro icon}} {{en icon}} {{fr icon}} | location = [[Mexico City]] | competitors = 82 | sports = 9 | flagbearer = | rank = 12 | gold = 4 | silver = 6 | bronze = 5 | officials = | appearances = auto | app_begin_year = 1900 | app_end_year = | summerappearances = | winterappearances = | seealso = }}
