{{Multiple issues| {{context|date=June 2018}} {{expand language|topic=|langcode=de|otherarticle=Shqipran Skeraj|date=June 2018}} |}} {{Infobox football biography | name = Shqipran Skeraj | fullname = Shqipran Skeraj | height = {{height|m=1.82|precision=0}} | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1985|11|24}} | birth_place = [[Prizren]], [[Socialist Federal Republic of Yugoslavia|SFR Yugoslavia]] | position = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]] | currentclub = | clubnumber = | youthyears1 = 1998–1999 | youthyears2 = 1999–2000 | youthyears3 = 2000–2001 | youthyears4 = 2001–2004 | youthclubs1 = NFC Rot-Weiß Berlin | youthclubs2 = [[NSC Marathon 02|Marathon 02]] | youthclubs3 = BSV Hürtürkel | youthclubs4 = [[FC Prishtina]] | years1 = 2004–2009 | years2 = 2007 | years3 = 2008–2009 | years4 = 2009–2010 | years5 = 2011 | years6 = 2011–2015 | years7 = 2014–2015 | years8 = 2015– | clubs1 = [[FC Prishtina]] | clubs2 = → [[KF Liria]] (loan) | clubs3 = → [[SpVgg Greuther Fürth|Greuther Fürth]] (loan) | clubs4 = [[TuS Koblenz]] | clubs5 = [[Djurgårdens IF Fotboll|Djurgården]] | clubs6 = [[SC Eltersdorf]] | clubs7 = [[SC Eltersdorf|SC Eltersdorf II]] | clubs8 = ATSV Erlangen | caps1 = | caps2 = | caps3 = 5 | caps4 = 19 | caps5 = 0 | caps6 = 79 | caps7 = 13 | caps8 = 5 | goals1 = | goals2 = | goals3 = 0 | goals4 = 0 | goals5 = 0 | goals6 = 1 | goals7 = 1 | goals8 = 0 | nationalyears1 = 2004– | nationalteam1 = [[Kosovo national football team|Kosovo]] | nationalcaps1 = 4 | nationalgoals1 = 0 | manageryears1 = 2014 | managerclubs1 = [[SC Eltersdorf|SC Eltersdorf U17]] | pcupdate = }}
'''Shqipran Skeraj''' ([[Serbo-Croatian|Serbo-Croat]]: ''Šćipran Skeraj'') (born 24 November 1985 in [[Prizren]]) is a [[Kosovo|Kosovar]] footballer who currently plays for ATSV Erlangen in the [[Bezirksliga Mittelfranken 1]], the seventh tier of football in Germany.
== Personal == Skeraj was born in [[Prizren]], [[Socialist Federal Republic of Yugoslavia|SFR Yugoslavia]] and raised in [[Berlin]]. His younger brother Agron Skeraj is also a professional footballer. He played on trial with Swedish side Djurgården during three months in 2011.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dif.se/2011/04/27/provspelare-fran-kosovo-pa-ingang/|title=Provspelare från Kosovo på ingång|last=Ernerot|first=Peder|date=27 April 2011|work=dif.se|publisher=Djurgårdens IF Fotboll|language=Swedish|accessdate=20 November 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110505235511/http://dif.se/2011/04/27/provspelare-fran-kosovo-pa-ingang/|archivedate=5 May 2011|df=dmy-all}}</ref>
