The '''Sinuiju Stadium''', also called the '''October Stadium''',<ref name="daum">http://cafe.daum.net/stade/5BXH/66?docid=1DZEG5BXH6620110407124655</ref> is a [[multi-purpose stadium]] in [[Sinuiju|Sinŭiju]], [[North Korea]], that is mainly used for events and [[football (soccer)|football]] matches of the [[Amrokkang Sports Club]]. Built in 1965, its capacity 17,500.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.worldstadiums.com/asia/countries/north_korea.shtml |title=Stadiums in North Korea |date=2013-05-20 |work= |publisher=World Stadiums |accessdate=2013-05-20 |quote= |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6GkmApn1e |archivedate=2013-05-20 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="daum"/>

